Interface OWLAnnotationValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<OWLObject>, OWLAnnotationObject, OWLObject, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    OWLAnonymousIndividual, OWLLiteral
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IRI, OWLAnonymousIndividualImpl, OWLLiteralImpl, OWLLiteralImplBoolean, OWLLiteralImplDouble, OWLLiteralImplFloat, OWLLiteralImplInteger, OWLLiteralImplNoCompression

    public interface OWLAnnotationValue
extends OWLAnnotationObject
    A marker interface for annotation values, which can either be an IRI (URI), Literal or Anonymous Individual, with visitor methods.
    Author:
    Matthew Horridge, The University of Manchester, Information Management Group, Date: 13-Jan-2009
    See Also:
    IRI, OWLLiteral, OWLAnonymousIndividual
